title: $:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/examples/collect-classify
tags: $:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/example
example-name: Collect & classify
example-description: Find untagged tiddlers and ask the LLM to suggest tags — result written to a temp tiddler
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

!! Collect & classify

Multi-tiddler context via arbitrary filter: the `untagged-tiddlers` template collects tiddlers with no tags. The `output-target` is a filter expression `[[$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/classification-result]]` that resolves to a temp tiddler.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, multi-tiddler context (arbitrary filter), `output-mode: text`, `output-target: <filter>`, `inject-as: user-message`, prompt template precedence

```
<$button>
  Classify untagged tiddlers
  <$llm-action
    promptTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/prompts/classify"
  />
</$button>
```

!!! Live demo

